nodes.text: Bombad Jedi is an article that was featured in StarWars Insider 199, published December 15, 2020. It is an interview of Ahmed Best conducted by Mark Newbold. It was first previewed five days prior in a December 10 StarWars.com article. The two discuss Best's experience of playing Jar Jar Binks in the Star Wars prequel trilogy as well as Jedi Master Kelleran Beq in Star Wars: Jedi Temple Challenge.
